data.description: You'll love this darling home supplying an abundance of open living space filled with surprising elements. A large living room off the entry provides a comfortable space to gather for great conversation with friends as sunlight filters through the large picture window; the low maintenance hardwood floors & brick fireplace add to the relaxing ambience of the room. Prospective buyers will love the spa-like main bathroom boasting a large jetted tub, separate shower & oversized vanity perfect for multiple people utilizing the space on busy mornings. In addition to the main floor master bedroom (with his-&-her closets), a huge 2nd master suite is located in the basement. This secluded oasis with dual-sink vanity & tile-surround jetted tub, sits separate from the stand-up shower, while a spacious walk-in closet offers extra shelving & built-in organization. This privately situated space provides all the conveniences necessary for total relaxation. A sprawling family room (with upgraded recessed lighting) delivers the ideal area to construct an in-home theater as well as a designated gaming area ??? this space will have you longing to spend your weekends relaxing at home. This wonderful home supplies upgraded amenities & features at an attractive price perfect for your growing household.
